dc_description_s: Insurance maps of Ambridge, Beaver County, Pennsylvania, Feb. 1911. 1 map on 15 sheets : col. ; 64 x 54 cm. Cadastral map.  Title from sheet [1].  Oriented with north to the upper right on some sheets.  Feby. 1911.""  Township of Economy noted on sheets 8 and 9; ""At French Point"" on sheet 10.  Includes sheet index map, street and ""Specials"" indexes, key, notes, and text."". Scale approximately 1:600. 50 ft. to an in.
